<section class="testimonials" aria-labelledby="story-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 id="story-heading" class="section-heading">OUR STORY</h2>
    <div>
      <p>
          Newark AI Town Hall was founded in 2024 by a group of educators, technologists, and
          community organizers who saw a growing gap between those who understand AI and those who
          don't. We recognized that this knowledge gap could deepen existing inequalities in our
          community.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Starting with small workshops at local libraries and community centers, we've grown into
          a vibrant community of learners, teachers, and advocates. Today, we serve hundreds of
          Newark residents each month through our programs and resources.
        </p>
      </div>

</section>

